</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="72r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l14">der Stat cʒu Augſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742062013_1723"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / daʒ vvir euch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l16">bey 
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l15"><expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> wiſſen laſſen 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſullen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l18"><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> wie wir vns halten wöllen von <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> leuffe vnd widerſages </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l20">wegen / als 
<del rend="strikethrough">an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber 
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742072103_1734">
<del rend="strikethrough">erber </del></ab></add> potſchaft </del> cʒu Coſtencʒ eruordert <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l21">Alſo laſʒen vvir ewr freuntſchaft wiſſen / daʒ dieſelb ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> potſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742079883_1744">von Coſtancʒ erſt am Oſterabent nehſt herheim cʒu vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l25">vnd vns ſölch leuff vnd gevverbe 
<del rend="strikethrough">erſt als </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742075008_1739">auff </ab></add> hewte 
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742082923_1749">erſt </ab></add> geſagt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l26">fürgelegt hat / darauff wir in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Rate noch nihts beſloſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l28"> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie vvir eʒ damit meinen cʒuhalten / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvan het </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l27"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wir </del> vver </ab></add> vvir dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l29">icht cʒerate worden oder heten ichts beſloſſen / das heten vvir euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l32">bey 
<del rend="strikethrough">dem <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1576742108948_1784"><expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> poten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wiſſen laſſen / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l34"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb vnd dinſte beweıſen möhten des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>will<ex>ig</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l35"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> die <expan>feſt<ex>um</ex></expan> paſce Anno etc xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="72r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Augspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, daz wir euch <add>bey
                                        <add><expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan></add>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan></add> wissen lassen
                                    <add><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, wie wir uns halten
                        wöllen von <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan> leuffe und widersages wegen, als
                        czu Costencz ervordert <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ist etc., also laszen
                        wir ewr freuntschaft wissen, daz dieselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        potschaft von Costancz erst am <app><note><q type="date">osterabent nehst</q>30.03.1415</note></app> herheim czu uns
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist und uns sölch leuff und gewerbe
                            <add>auff</add> hewte <add>erst</add> gesagt und fürgelegt hat. Darauff
                        wir in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate noch nihts beslossen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wie wir ez damit meinen czu halten,
                                    <add><expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wer</add> wir davon icht cze
                        rate worden oder heten ichts beslossen, das heten wir euch bey
                                    <add><expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> poten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wissen
                        lassen. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir ewr
                            <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinste beweisen möhten, des
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>will<ex>ig</ex></expan> etc.
                                D<expan>at<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> die <expan>fest<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        pasce anno etc. xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi>. </ab>
</div>
